===== Host interface =====

This class is designed to work with host interfaces. 

Object references: \\
  * [[manual:api:reference:hostinterface:object#host_interface|Host interface]]

Available methods: \\

  * ''[[manual:api:reference:hostinterface:create|hostinterface.create]]'' - creating new host interfaces
  * ''[[manual:api:reference:hostinterface:delete|hostinterface.delete]]'' - deleting host interfaces
  * ''[[manual:api:reference:hostinterface:get|hostinterface.get]]'' - retrieving host interfaces
  * ''[[manual:api:reference:hostinterface:massadd|hostinterface.massadd]]'' - adding host interfaces to hosts
  * ''[[manual:api:reference:hostinterface:massremove|hostinterface.massremove]]'' - removing host interfaces from hosts
  * ''[[manual:api:reference:hostinterface:replacehostinterfaces|hostinterface.replacehostinterfaces]]'' - replacing host interfaces on a host
  * ''[[manual:api:reference:hostinterface:update|hostinterface.update]]'' - updating host interfaces
